data.description: This charming 2-story, 3BR, 2.5 BA is located in the sought out Luckey Neighborhood in Northwest San Antonio. The like-new home (sold AS IS) has been remodeled with new flooring, black appliances, and it has a nice back yard for family gatherings. Home is move-in ready and access to Lackland AFB and Sea World are in close proximity. Come by and see it today you will not be disappointed!
